extends javax.swing.JPanel

      • EntryTab

        public EntryTab(Entry en)
        Creates an EntryTab using an Entry object. Also initializes the HTMLEditorPane and toolbar. First call to this method is expensive as it spins up the entirety of HTMLEditorPane
        Parameters:
        en - Entry to be displayed.
